Osman Gani is a Musical Artist. He was born on 02 January 1997 in Chittagong, Bangladesh. Osman Gani is a young Musician in the music industry. With the rapid growth and modernization of technology in the twenty-first century, young minds are inspired to create new and inspiring ideas that can make a huge difference in today’s technology. One such example is Osman Gani. Who, through his knowledge and hard work, is gifting new music to the world. Musician in Bangladesh did not show any age limit
